commit_message:
Code refactor for demo

* information.csv --> only for printing the table with the code (for demo);
* main.py --> for CA, only getting first 5 columns; only_ca (removing Ness_result column); decision engine is writing its own table in auth/decision_table); quarantine is unlocking the blocking and printing an exception if nothing to do
* main_with.py --> creating mutual object to get ID (this could be probably improved), added exception on exchange table; change name of function to sbeat;
* mutual.py --> added own identity to the table by default;
* ness_main.py --> added some modifications to get_table to make it compatible with decision engine input; creating good server list table with all the nodes as bening;
* secret.txt --> added for demo;
* server.py --> reading shared secret from secret.txt;
* server-demo.py --> flask server to show both tables;
* utils.py (continuous) --> added ID in the update table on ca; added exception on the ca_client;
* utils.py (features) --> server now save the table on file

